---
title: Chipotle Barbacoa Tacos with Quick-Pickled Onions and Salad
description: We're bringing the taqueria home tonight! This easy dinner comes together in a cinch, without the time and effort of a slow-cooker. Packed with rich and smoky flavours, this meal will have you dreaming of your next Mexican vacation.
